The Sideline 2015 "Game of the Week" is Columbia at Bolles. 
Sports Director Chris Porter and Chad Cushnir will be on the campus of Bolles School on Friday, October 9th. 
Our "Game of the Week" coverage starts Friday afternoon at 5 and continues at 5:30, 6, 7, and 11. Read or Share this story: http://fcnews.tv/1Lj4dav TOP VIDEOS
